---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="hestia · about">
  <Section eyebrow="§ about" title="frontend, volunteer.">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <aside class="about-aside">
        <dl>
          <dt>stack</dt>
          <dd>astro 6, typescript strict, vanilla css</dd>
          <dt>currently</dt>
          <dd>community manager @ gamevox</dd>
          <dt>learning</dt>
          <dd>full stack, cybersecurity, data analytics</dd>
        </dl>
      </aside>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>i'm a frontend developer. i build ui components, layouts, and design systems.</p>
        <p>most of my work is volunteer. it happens on gamevox, a privacy-focused voice chat platform, where i design and prototype interface mockups, contribute to community resources, and shape the user experience.</p>
        <p>what i ship, i'm willing to defend. privacy-first by default; no trackers, no analytics, no cookies.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>
